AGENT AUDIT (unreviewed — treat claims as unverified)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

C++ header: include/emCore/emRef.h
C++ implementation: src/emCore/emRef.cpp

C++ public API:
  - class emRefTarget
    - emRefTarget()                              // construct with zero refcount
    - virtual ~emRefTarget()                     // fatal error if refcount != 0
    - emRefTarget(const emRefTarget&)            // copy ctor; does NOT copy refcount
    - emRefTarget& operator=(const emRefTarget&) // assignment; does NOT copy refcount
    - void Alloc()                               // increment refcount
    - void Free()                                // decrement refcount; delete this if <= 0
    - int GetRefCount() const                    // return refcount

  - template<class CLS> class emRef
    - emRef()                                    // NULL reference
    - emRef(const emRef&)                        // copy; calls Alloc on target
    - emRef(CLS* model)                          // from raw ptr; calls Alloc
    - ~emRef()                                   // calls Free on target
    - emRef& operator=(const emRef&)             // rebind; Alloc new, Free old
    - void Set(CLS* model = NULL)                // rebind to raw ptr
    - emRef& operator=(CLS* model)               // rebind to raw ptr
    - void Reset()                               // Set(NULL)
    - operator CLS*() const                      // implicit conversion to raw ptr
    - CLS* Get() const                           // explicit get raw ptr
    - CLS* operator->() const                    // smart-pointer dereference

