  - emScreen.h:53: static emRef<emScreen> LookupInherited(...) (return type)
  - emSigModel.h:44: static emRef<emSigModel> Acquire(...) (return type)
  - emCoreConfig.h:37: static emRef<emCoreConfig> Acquire(...) (return type)
  - emCoreConfigPanel.h:57: emRef<emCoreConfig> Config (member variable)
  - emFileModel.h:309: emRef<emSigModel> (member variable in PSAgentClass context)
  - emVarModel.h: extensive use in template Acquire/Get/Set methods
  - emVarSigModel.h: extensive use in template methods
  - emFpPlugin.cpp:120,170: emRef<emModel>, emRef<emFpPluginList> (return types, locals)
